South Africans who shop online value one aspect of online shopping more than others – and that’s excellent delivery and payments processing. This is according to the 2018 MyBroadband Online Shopping Survey. The survey was taken by 1,268 tech-savvy South Africans, many of whom are MyBroadband readers and forum members. Survey participants were asked “What is the most important aspect of a good online store?” and the results of the answers are detailed in the table below. The question was single-choice only. Survey participants were also asked “What is your preferred payment method when shopping online?” Respondent were asked to select their preferred payment method, and the results of the answers are detailed in the table below. The question was single-choice only.